{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Soul Drifter is an atmospheric single-player first-person platformer set in a surreal underwater world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/GIF1_low_cut.gif?t=1730033945\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re a fallen angel in an unfamiliar world. Master your skills to save captive souls in this atmospheric adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gravity-Defying Parkour</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soar into heart-pounding parkour runs on courses only possible for someone with wings. Rack up airtime as you glide across vast chasms, dash through obstacles, and flap your wings for a powerful double jump. String together moves and enter a flow state in which you\u2019ll barely need to touch the ground. Just manage your stamina carefully \u2014 there\u2019s nothing to catch you if you fall.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/GIF2_low_B.gif?t=1730033945\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Master the Machines</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on fast-paced parkour courses that put your new skills to the test. Muster your courage to enter the final challenge of each level \u2014 a massive factory that will challenge both your movement accuracy and reaction time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/GIF3_low_D.gif?t=1730033945\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Strange Landscapes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a surreal, unfamiliar world. Encounter wide open underwater vistas, narrow factory corridors, and towering structures meant to communicate with the gods. Why are other souls kept imprisoned here \u2014 and what did their captors intend to do with them?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Glide through the air by mastering the stamina system</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Activate special moves like dashes and double jumps</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore levels in a great variety of different biomes, from natural vistas to dangerous factories</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect hidden data tablets to learn more about the strange world you've landed in</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat difficult &quot;boss&quot; levels at the end of each area to save your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Adventure begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/3cd2918bcc57c30ac481220738f99fde4565523a.jpg"},{"name":"The Sewers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/0ba4b7ff1a7a22caedde007754306e5f29a7485c.jpg"},{"name":"The Mines","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/e77802375587c857462d8ebd36bf85b805bba8a9.jpg"},{"name":"Cryo Chambers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/868a044f20fd34dbf5c93e6009f4e9365de61873.jpg"},{"name":"The End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/b9fdd50220e6e73626390ece5089a42a0f6378b0.jpg"},{"name":"Entomophobia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/b506c9f4865f1a5c1bc83253770f336f821c8309.jpg"},{"name":"The floor is lava","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2553930/d224bfbdcfc850a29ea5336